    <p>Toolshed is just getting started, and we need your help!  We're coming up short on good slogans we can use for advertising.  Enter your suggestion- we'll try running it, and if it's one of the top three performing slogans, you'll get a crisp $50 bill in the mail!  Look around the site some- they best slogans will do a good gob at reflecting Toolshed.  Facebook ads are limited to 70 characters (enter in the top form), if you have any additional advice concerning how to run the ad, use the bottom field.  Winners will be chosen May 1- good Luck!</p><br/>


